STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Harry CAMPBELL, Jr., Defendant-Petitioner. C-249 September Term 2017
079392 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 26, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003518-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
